  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.end_expansion_guide.name": "HP 末地扩展手册",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.end_expansion_guide.landing_text": "记录 HP 末地扩展中的生物外观、名称、机制与生成方式。$(br2)本手册会随内容继续补充。",
