  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.category.creatures.name": "末地生物",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.category.creatures.description": "HP 末地扩展加入的生物、宠物与生态小帮手。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.overview.name": "生物总览",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.overview.page.ecology.title": "末地生态",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.overview.page.ecology.text": "$(entity)虚空鲸$() 是巨型可骑乘生物；$(entity)末影盒$() 是可携带的宠物容器；$(entity)末影蜗牛$() 会管理紫颂植物并产出蜗牛壳。$(br2)三者都围绕末地探索、收纳和紫颂自动化展开。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.overview.page.pet_bag.title": "宠物袋",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.overview.page.pet_bag.text": "$(mechanic)宠物袋$() 可右键收容可驯服宠物，便于迁移与整理。对已经收纳了生物的宠物袋，手持右键方块可重新实体化。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.name": "虚空鲸",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.entity.name": "虚空鲸",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.appearance.text": "$(entity)虚空鲸$() 是末地高空中的巨型虚空生物，身体庞大，适合远距离观察。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.mechanics.title": "机制",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.mechanics.text": "$(mechanic)驯服：$()未驯服时用末影珍珠互动，累计进度后会被驯服。$(br)$(mechanic)骑乘：$()主人直接右键即可骑乘。骑乘时按移动输入控制方向，下潜可用潜行键。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.pearl.title": "珍珠与传送",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.pearl.text": "骑乘时手持末影珍珠，移动速度额外提升。虚空鲸每秒有小概率吃掉玩家手中的一颗末影珍珠。$(br2)骑乘者可消耗末影珍珠进行水平远距传送，传送主要改变 XZ 轴。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.spawn.title": "生成",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.void_whale.page.spawn.text": "$(spawn)生成：$()虚空鲸自然生成在末地生物群系标签中，权重较低，每次通常只出现 1 只。$(br2)已驯服虚空鲸会尽量保持在主人 48 格范围内。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.name": "末影盒",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.entity.name": "末影盒",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.appearance.text": "$(entity)末影盒$() 是会行走的末地储物宠物，外观接近带生命感的盒状容器。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.mechanics.title": "机制",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.mechanics.text": "$(mechanic)驯服：$()用紫颂果右键喂食。驯服后会跟随玩家，并在初始容器中获得一次末地船风格战利品。$(br2)右键已驯服末影盒可打开 54 格容器。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.pack.title": "收纳与放出",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.pack.text": "主人潜行右键末影盒，可把它和内部物品一起收纳成物品。手持末影盒物品右键方块，可重新放出实体。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.spawn.title": "生成",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_box.page.spawn.text": "$(spawn)生成：$()末影盒不是普通自然刷新的野外生物，主要通过刷怪蛋、物品重新实体化或后续结构内容获得。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.name": "末影蜗牛",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.entity.name": "末影蜗牛",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.appearance.text": "$(entity)末影蜗牛$() 是紫颂园丁，壳上会逐渐长出紫颂晶簇。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.chorus.title": "紫颂管理",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.chorus.text": "末影蜗牛会主动爬向成熟紫颂植株并啃食整株。未驯服蜗牛只清理植株并重新留下紫颂花；已驯服蜗牛会把产物掉落或放入附近容器。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.tame.title": "驯服与催熟",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.tame.text": "$(mechanic)驯服：$()紫颂果有概率驯服末影蜗牛。$(br2)驯服蜗牛会寻找附近未成熟紫颂花，用身体蹭植株并显著加速紫颂树生长，催生时紫颂花会冒出末影粒子。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.growth.title": "成长与繁殖",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.growth.text": "新生成末影蜗牛约九成为幼体，一成为成年。幼体第十次长出紫颂晶簇时会长大一圈、掉落末影蜗牛壳，并变成成年个体。$(br2)同一主人驯服的成年蜗牛可用紫颂花繁殖。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.shell.title": "末影蜗牛壳",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.shell.text": "蜗牛壳不再通过击杀蜗牛获得。它来自幼体蜕变。$(br2)蜗牛壳可与盔甲合成，提供一次濒死保护：随机传送到周围安全位置，并按壳层数回复生命。",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.spawn.title": "生成",
  "patchouli.hp_end_expansion.entry.ender_snail.page.spawn.text": "$(spawn)生成：$()末影蜗牛自然生成在末地生物群系标签中，权重高于虚空鲸，每次通常出现 1 到 2 只。"
}
